== Headline ==

A [[transformation]] that is essentially driven by the types of affected data

== Description ==

Transformations may be arbitrarily complicated in how they transform given data. A [[type-driven transformation]] is relatively simple (and common) in so far that it only cares about specific types for the windows of transformation.

== Illustration ==

[[Feature:Cut]] illustrates the concept of [[type-driven transformation]].

